snippet.title: Counter Clash - Economy update
snippet.description:
The economy update for Counter Clash is live on the demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2838160/Counter_Clash/

Clear forests to make room for your farms, or create a trade route across the entire map. Just watch out for any raiders that like a share of the profit!

The economy update also includes various visual updates, bug fixes, and gameplay improvements.

#gaming #rts #indiegame #counterclash
